{"tid":1660532,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求助，如何提升工作表現？","createTime":"2019-10-17T14:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:10:33.000Z","uid":192929,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce2260811837c4bcee9c97faa0531bdae71eaf5","tid":1660532,"uid":192929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"番左工都成個月，都仲係乜都要問，十個step永遠做少一兩個。老細好有心咁教，但係佢講完我都仲可以改唔好。依家越做越冇自信，好驚累到老細。有冇人可以指點下我，我真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692421251adee1c2e4fc5f44f929173194fd9684","tid":1660532,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"09107b3f2818ff6c80308d473fc581c54b7338c2","tid":1660532,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"要求加人工<br />\n再比多d力"},{"pid":"ce43b8fc78bda03e7788831a921edc213296b154","tid":1660532,"uid":76365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n明明d嘢係識，但成日做漏少少比人周"},{"pid":"c4903768e0a3b60a4054a82b58bdc5702d16bb75","tid":1660532,"uid":78039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"checklist，訓多d"},{"pid":"32ab979339ada9382488cd51ff597d6106e58d4f","tid":1660532,"uid":237465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1ce2260811837c4bcee9c97faa0531bdae71eaf5","tid":1660532,"uid":192929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"番左工都成個月，都仲係乜都要問，十個step永遠做少一兩個。老細好有心咁教，但係佢講完我都仲可以改唔好。依家越做越冇自信，好驚累到老細。有冇人可以指點下我，我真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:30:27.000Z","msg":"好簡單.  以後問完咩問題.  即時寫低佢, 為自己的工作做本簡單 MANUAL, <br />\n有空的時候就翻閱一下, 唔明就最好問到明, 唔好自己去估. 因為隨時會估錯<br />\n唔好太心急去完成任務. 有時越急越錯.<br />\n用心去做.  做完再 DOUBLE CHECK 一下.   減少犯錯的機會.  自然就會<br />\n提升到表現<br />\nGood Luck"},{"pid":"e0f93e19af7ce1304fb5d5c4bec217c98797edd1","tid":1660532,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"on9老闆當你奴工炸<br />\n<br />\n工作量咁重仲覺得自己先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a9bb3e4275d8282d89b478fe5d2e5f37ce095d","tid":1660532,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"交貨前，自己check 多兩三次，老細邊教就邊記notes <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUkniOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUkniOv.jpg&h=8356bed2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3bd9Vb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3bd9Vb.jpg&h=bb6946ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuGmzmR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuGmzmR.jpg&h=ffc74dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOAiBAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOAiBAc.jpg&h=fd5a55fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PABBosY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPABBosY.png&h=9ee4fe34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONTW7UZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONTW7UZ.jpg&h=1d0cb166&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e60382c85fe05c4fec9908d0e8fa89b15fc95263","tid":1660532,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0f93e19af7ce1304fb5d5c4bec217c98797edd1","tid":1660532,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"on9老闆當你奴工炸<br />\n<br />\n工作量咁重仲覺得自己先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01563e1abe2930355c9cfcf6dca6ece5e6d8e4d3","tid":1660532,"uid":129698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"我同一份工返咗4年，今朝先問完點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情況同你一樣"},{"pid":"6401ee9ba5d168b42c44dd754d3c49127e5bbffa","tid":1660532,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"人地教你野，你有冇寫低啊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫低左，做完望實個list check多次，咁咪唔會再錯囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91b2d004e959702055e4da7bc64bacbb68b036c","tid":1660532,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"自己jot notes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e646948d1f9969d072f17b71884e9badca91be9d","tid":1660532,"uid":311660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"如果主要問題係漏step，前輩教嘅時候，寫低steps同要注意乜，唔好怕醜，有心教嘅會等你記好一個step再繼續講。<br />\n<br />\n用checklist 確保自己做嘅時候跟足step。<br />\n<br />\n有時間就模擬個流程一次，但小心唔好真係落咗單/ 做不能取消的步驟。冇得真做嘅，都要係個腦到run一次流程。<br />\n<br />\n虛心有禮地問，唔好怕醜，尤其你話上司好肯教。儲埋問題一次過問，見佢冇忙緊就可以問。<br />\n<br />\n咁幾時問人，幾時自己諗呢? 如果研究咗15分鐘都冇方向零頭緒，就問啦。<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228dffcdf99a006d33b52855b1c105933526b7fb","tid":1660532,"uid":226785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"Me too<br />\n好驚過唔到試用"},{"pid":"acc25096bfd51f852fd9c01146f0c57e62dc0815","tid":1660532,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"中出女上司/上司老婆/女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"